Backend
-------
npm init -y
npm install express dotenv
npm install nodemon
https://clerk.com/docs/expressjs/getting-started/quickstart
npm install @clerk/express
npm install cloudinary@2.8.0
npm install inngest

MongoDB
-------
Security > Database & Network Access > IP Access List > Allow Access From Anywhere
npm install mongoose@8.19.3

Admin
-----
npm create vite@latest .
npm install @clerk/clerk-react

Mobile
------
npx create-expo-app@latest .
rm -rf .git
ctrl + shift P then select Developer: Reload Window
git init on the main folder